    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Ninjutsu (Doton)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 3 (Spell Level 2)</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 1</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 16 | <b>Successes:</b> 2</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 4 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 16</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> H</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>The target square(s) must be composed of rock or dirt, which immediately shapes into small but sharp spikes and counts as though it had caltrops scattered over it (see p64). A square of makibishi has Defense 11, 3 HP and 8 hardness. When you dismiss this technique, you may choose to either dismiss all makibishi, or only a select number, leaving the rest (which could be dismissed at a later time).</p>\n\n\n\n",
